      "comment": "ALTA BILLY (3) hasn't fired in three runs back from a long stint on the sidelines but they have all been in stronger company and his fitness will be building. Enjoys a class drop on his last attempt at Menangle and should enjoy an economical run from this draw. Could show his best. CHARLIES ACE NZ (2) is better placed having come from this barrier for a 1.8m second the last time she raced here. Big chance. BETTING STAR (5) is working towards another win having registered another good performance here last time when coming from this barrier for second. Contender. WHEREISHE (4) must be respected having only once missed the top-three in his last six starts, coming from the back row to place last week.",
